data.description: HOME FOR THE HOLIDAYS! MOVE IN NOW-better than new construction! NEW ROOF AND GUTTERS! MASSIVE 24x24 Timber-tech Composite deck. Lots of storage/custom bookcases & craft desk or could be cool butler's pantry/entertaining space. Check out built-in kennel, located in mudroom! Upgraded luxury vinyl plank-1st floor. Living room could be office, playroom-great flex room to meet your needs. Kitchen & breakfast room opens to  fabulous deck & flows into great room. Cozy up in front of the fireplace flanked by built-in bookcases. Large bay window in expands the 1st floor! Upstairs, 3 spacious bedroom w/full walk-in closets. Coffered ceiling in master bedroom, plus walk-in closet & master bath w/an abundance of storage. Basement offers a private office & walk-out patio & accesses deck. Basement is ready for your ideas-roughed in for plumbing. Great family friendly neighborhood, located in Rockwood Schools & near beautiful new library & amenities of Eureka. Sellers are MOTIVATED-bring an offer.
